room_title: Escape room "Submerged" by North Texas Escape Rooms in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: We did the Submerged theme with a group of adults and it was a blast! Lucas, our host, did a great job explaining and giving us clues when we needed one! We would recommend to all our friends!

room_title: Escape room "Submerged" by North Texas Escape Rooms in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: We did the Submerged room and absolutely loved it. It was well prepared and had lots of details. Our escape master was awesome. Everyone in my group had a blast. We escaped with 4 minutes remaining. It was intense, but so much fun!
